Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a little late, but happy New Year!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please cheer us on a lot this year too, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. How did\Nyou all spend your New Year's?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shrine visits? Special New\NYear's meals? New Year's gifts?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, as for myself, I'm not\Nin jolly spirits much this year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My sister was born this year,\Nand it's our first New Year's all together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.53,0:00:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But as I am now, not able to do anything...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know it's not okay to let\Nthings stay like this, but, but, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:02.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa aka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:09.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:16.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:24.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:32.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:38.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:42.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:46.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:02:02.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' Can't stop lovin' U\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:10.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in U hikikae ni subete ushinatte mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:17.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' Can't stop lovin' U\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, you did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you following up Layla and Yuri, we\Nwon the competition twice consecutively.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to start rehearsing for the New\NYear's show right away, starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This show will be your triumphal performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Needless to say, we're going to\Nuse the Demon Spiral for the climax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Mia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... How about Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is going to appear on stage with us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because as far as I'm concerned,\Nthe festival contest isn't over yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you withdrew. You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You disgraced the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ran away from the stage\Nwhere a serious match was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also a place where you\Ndestroy the dreams of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told myself that I would fight to the finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for the trouble I caused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Amazing and Sad Homecoming."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Sora just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're removing Sora from\Nthe New Year's show cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now I've come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't shock me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least call if you're coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.03,0:06:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... I thought...\NSince it's the New Year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, doesn't your next rehearsal start soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I decided to skip it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skip it? Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yume's gotten so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Yume. It's your big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought that once\Nmy mother had a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There would be no room for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, both your mother\Nand her baby are trying hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cheer them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you name the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted you to name my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Yume. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to you, I feel like\NI finally became a part of the family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both my mother and father\Nwere hoping for me to come home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I'll just stay here from now on.\NI won't go back to the stage anymore...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Mia... Isn't she one of\Nyour friends I met over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Mia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Oh... That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave without telling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Uh... there was a lot of\Nstuff I wanted to think over, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you are coming back, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I'm fine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, everyone, don't worry about me. Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I never expected you'd be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long can you stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was thinking of taking\Nmy time and staying for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, can you get me another beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole family's gathered after a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right to cut loose\Nevery once in a while, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:08:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me of the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a nice room.\NIt just looks like it belongs to a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, did you hide in my luggage again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to come to Japan once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I have to check\Nout the {\i1}geisha {\i0}and the {\i1}kogals{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting your time staying with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stage... I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really decide\Nthat you're not going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the answer will\Nmake itself known naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've given up the stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,soon you'll no longer be able to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Spiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mia. I'm sure Sora will be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't give instructions, I won't know\Nhow the show's supposed to fit together, will I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to drag me and Leon down?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not interested in this, quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?!\NActing like she is so important...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact of the matter is,\Nshe became No. 1 in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's full of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end of the year is getting close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much has happened this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.82,0:10:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. It's sad to say\Ngoodbye to this year, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is even more lavish\Nthan our usual New Year's feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, your {\i1}ozouni {\i0}soup really is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is the town where Sora lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to come here all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time to space out.\NDidn't you come here to see Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the only thing I know is her address.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how the\Nroads here work or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a police officer. Let me handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, why don't you take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, one should begin a new\Nyear by cleansing one's body and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:12:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool, how long are you going to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going back to Kaleido Stage anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you find somebody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you still training?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... this is my after-meal exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I think you should take a\Nshower after your exercise and feel clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you have a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you could say\Nthat this is very Japanese too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kurata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Manami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami... How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this! If you're\Nback, you could at least call!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be there with Sayaka and Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's have a New Year's party at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? Japan has a bunch of weirdoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no, I think that's a natural reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we help you with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think he looks super cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Maybe he's a foreign\Nsoccer player or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he must be a movie star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this! Take a picture, a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a picture with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.99,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind taking one more picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... I haven't seen you guys in a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... But, I never expected\NSora would really go to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, nobody believes something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:14:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I've heard that being\Na Kaleido Star was your dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami, you saw Sora's show, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I saw that legendary great maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how should I describe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt as if I was flying in the sky with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange, but I felt some kind of\Nenergy through my body as I watched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting to play the leading parts and\Nstuff from the very beginning, I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka joined a voice actors' agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... That's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you do anime voices and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, in the last round of auditions\NI made it to final callbacks for the lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't get the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't get so down.\NThere'll be other shows!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it means I need\Nto improve my skills more, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you wanted\Nto be a manga artist, right Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to junior college and get a\Njob after that like everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to keep drawing manga as my hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miki, you're good at manga!\NThat's such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, when it becomes your job,\Nyou have a lot of tough times, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think if I went through that,\NI'd end up hating manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to keep loving manga forever, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like you,\NMiki, you're such a realist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how about you, Sora? You made\Nyour dream come true really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why do you look so gloomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... How should I say this?\NSee, I have many reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't you do something and show us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a good idea since it's a new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... You're so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh... This applause...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's different from when I was in the festival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what is different. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The audience applauds for the same reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I am the one who's different?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm enjoying it now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm enjoying it with Manami\Nand the rest of my friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. The shows that everybody enjoys,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that's the Kaleido Stage I like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanted to be in more shows like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you're a real pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we have to go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I will come to see your show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I've decided to go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I gave up a\Ndream to be a hair stylist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to take time and\Ntalk with my parents and decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:17:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started thinking like this thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was watching you working so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started wanting to chase after my dream too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you gave me a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you came back to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have something to do with the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you quit in the middle of your\Nperformance at the Circus Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I found out about it on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.45,0:17:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Well, that's not the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a phone call from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked me to spend time with you to\Ndivert your mind, since you looked upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be worried about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran out on Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you don't have any regrets about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd rather just do\Nsomething than think about it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you didn't want thinking\Nabout it to make you hesitate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you end up not\Ndoing it and regretting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always said that,\Never since we were in school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you don't regret your decision,\NI have no problems with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you're regretting it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why not try doing your\Nbest to give it another shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should just shamelessly tell them\N"I changed my mind and want to come back!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you can\Ndo things like that, Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I met you in America,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I came to see\Nyour regretful face. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may think I'm selfish,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want to see your regretful face now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll end up leaving without seeing her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Biting someone's head all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me because\NI don't understand Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't watch out, you'll be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora! I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought Ken along too, as sort of an extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Extra"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I keep worrying everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've basically wrapped up\Nthe New Year's show rehearsals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to try coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's show?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's May and Leon's triumphal performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the opening day is\Ntomorrow, I have to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But we just met up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, we already\Npurchased the airline tickets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are coming back, aren't you, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora... I hope you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I am now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if I come back to Kaleido Stage,\NI'm afraid I'll get in everybody's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you dropped out of the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually a little relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I think in that situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,crying and not being able to\Ngo on is more like the Sora I know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than being totally fine with it\Nall and being able to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you create a show without them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Create one? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see more of\Nyour cheerful, fun shows, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, when you're flying\Nthrough the air looking so bright, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you lots too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like to see you like that too.\NI like it lots and lots and lots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As your number one fan, I want\Nto see a Sora show like that soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mr. Number Two Fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fans like us always love Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... What I meant was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We love Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to create a fun\NKaleido Stage with no battles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my dream, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can become a true Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the answers are inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going after your dream without being lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, I'm sure the road to\Nbeing a real Kaleido Star will open for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:21:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to create a Kaleido Stage\Nwith no battles that's fun for everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is my real dream. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I do that, the road to being a\Nreal Kaleido Star should open there too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go back to Kaleido Stage\None more time. I will for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you do, we'll come\Nto the airport to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... I see. I think that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Manami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's why I came back this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry it's such a pathetic story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... After thinking a lot,\NI feel like going back there. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, since you didn't even visit\Na shrine early in the new year...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good luck charm...
